casebody.data:
Wednesday, February 17, 1999

MERIT DOCKET

98-2615. State ex rel. Howard v. Weiher.

Lucas App. No. L-98-1344. On motion to dismiss and motion for award of reasonable expenses. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, F.E. Sweeney, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., concurs and would also award attorney fees. Resnick, J., not participating.
